      <item recommended="false">
	<name>pidgin-otr</name>
	<summary>"Off The Record" end-to-end encryption plugin for gaim</summary>
	<description>This is a gaim plugin which implements Off-the-Record (OTR) Messaging. OTR allows you to have private conversations over IM by providing:
- Encryption
- No one else can read your instant messages.
- Authentication
- You are assured the correspondent is who you think it is.
- Deniability
- The messages you send do _not_ have digital signatures that are checkable by a third party. Anyone can forge messages after a conversation to make them look like they came from you. However, _during_ a conversation, your correspondent is assured the messages he sees are authentic and unmodified.
- Perfect forward secrecy
- If you lose control of your private keys, no previous conversation is compromised.</description>
      </item>
